        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A well-trained maraquoi hunter can launch themself at their prey from any perch, in any direction. You [[/act high-jump]], [[/act long-jump]], or [[/act maneuver-in-flight]] to @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Fly] your fly Speed. If you move at least 10 feet and end in a square adjacent to a target, make a melee Strike or attempt to [[/act shove]] the target. If you rolled a critical success on your Athletics check to High Jump or a success on your Acrobatics check to Maneuver in Flight, your target is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Off-Guard] to this attack.</p>"
        },
